november candidates selected by robert france and list sent to the inria international affairs dpt december list of candidates sent by the partner institutions is posted and selection is made by the internship managers january following year circulation of the final selection financing graduate students coming to inria on the reussi programme will receive 1100 euros 1500us in each month of their internships 50 by international affairs dpt and 50 by the host team the monthly stipend is tax exempt and students will also receive health insurance the nsf will fund air travel for selected students 2007 2012 stanford university 216 encina hall west stanford ca 94305 6045 phone 650.736 1321 fax 650.723 3010 ica information stanford edu drupal hit counter
